source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_000<tab>Ah, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>! Come to admire the fruits of your labor, eh?

TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_001<tab>I reckon you'll be singin' a song in your heart when you see what this place has become, all through the efforts of you and your fellow skybuilders. Go on─take it all in.
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_001<tab>Ça y est<var 1D /var>! La con<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion du Nouveau Refrain est enfin achevée<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_002<tab>As Francel doubtless told you, Risensong's to be the new center of culture and aesthetic appreciation here in the Firmament.
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_002<tab>C'est un lieu où l'on peut s'épanouir dans un environnement culturel riche et varié.

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_003<tab>It's a place where nobles and commonfolk alike can now partake in the finer pleasures of life, like a soothing dip in the waters at Snowsoak Springs. We also have a brand-new infirmary, where those sufferin' from all manner of injuries and ailments can get the care they need.
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_003<tab>On y trouve par exemple une maison de repos et des bains publics que tous peuvent fréquenter, nobles comme roturiers.

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_004<tab>Now, typically this would be where I tell you to not to wander off, what with our next buildin' project awaitin' on the agenda. But─and I can scarce believe I'm sayin' this─our work here has finally come to an end.
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_004<tab>Sur ces belles paroles, j'ai l'honneur de vous déclarer que le grand chantier de recon<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion d'Azurée est of<var 16 /var>fi<var 16 /var>ciel<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment terminé<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_005<tab>Aye, you heard me right. The rebirth of the Risensong Quarter marks the culmination of the restoration project in its entirety. I'm sure you'll agree that we've wrought somethin' wonderful here. Truly, I can't thank you enough for lendin' your skills and labor to the cause.
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_005<tab>Admirez notre magnifique quartier, flamboyant à nouveau dans le ciel du Coerthas alors qu'il n'était plus qu'un champ de pierres après la guerre<var 1D /var>! C'est grâce à vos efforts, et ceux d'artisans du monde entier<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_006<tab>Hm? What are you all standin' about for? Isn't there work what needs doin' somewhere?
TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_ENIE_000_007<tab>Oh, come now, Augebert. Who gave you a monopoly on the company of our favorite skybuilder? We simply wished to express our gratitude as well.
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_ENIE_000_007<tab>Hé hé, on est venus dire deux mots à <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_POTKIN_000_009<tab>Though the reconstruction effort itself may be complete, we hope that you'll grace us with your presence from time to time. After all, we will still have need of various and sundry materials for maintenance and upkeep. Pray don't be a stranger!
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_POTKIN_000_009<tab>S'il vous reste des matériaux sur les bras, ou si vous vous sentez désœuvré<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>, n'hésitez pas à nous rendre visite<var 1D /var>! Il nous en faudra sûrement pour tout ce qui est retouches, finitions et tout le tintouin<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_LIZBETH_000_010<tab>Indeed. Should you be so inclined, the Kupo of Fortune will always be here to smile upon you, my friend.
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_LIZBETH_000_010<tab>Et si vous êtes devenu<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> accro au Kupo de la fortune, je serai toujours là pour satisfaire vos pulsions pour le jeu<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_LUDOVRAINT_000_011<tab>And should you deign to assist us from time to time, it will be my pleasure and honor both to continue to keep a record of your many accomplishments, that they might be remembered by all who would follow you.
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_LUDOVRAINT_000_011<tab>J'ai longtemps attendu votre arrivée, mais pas votre départ. Si vous daignez rester, vous continuerez pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment à accumuler des points d'azur. Dans tous les cas, je continuerai de les comptabiliser et de tenir le classement à jour<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_FLOTPASSANT_100_011<tab>Truly, we have nothing but gratitude for you and your fellow artisans. What once the people of this nation could never have dreamed, you have made a reality!
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_FLOTPASSANT_100_011<tab>Merci beaucoup<var 1D /var>! Nous en serions encore à déblayer l'esplanade sans vous et vos collègues<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_012<tab>But what are we standin' about here for? I don't know about the rest of you, but I'm in the mood for celebratin'─an' lookin' at the faces of the people around us, I'm far from the only one.
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_012<tab>Ha ha ha, pas de repos pour les braves, hein<var 1D /var>? L'ambiance est à la fête, laissez un peu vos outils de côté<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_013<tab>Meanwhile, I reckon Francel's just itchin' to share his thoughts with you, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. If you've got a moment to spare, why not pay him a call? Till we meet again!
target: TEXT_LUCKHA031_04042_AUGEBERT_000_013<tab>Je ne sais pas si vous avez croisé Francel, mais lui ne tient plus en place<var 1D /var>! Passez donc le voir quand vous aurez un peu de temps<var 1D /var>!
